These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, juice, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, chess, cooking, dancing
1. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is chess##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
3. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
4. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | juice | milk       | almond-milk | soy-milk        |
| Hobby      | cooking  | chess | dancing        | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, fish, turtle, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, climbing, handball, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the owner of the turtle##7
2. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
3. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | turtle | fish       | rat         | lizard     |
| Sport   | climbing   | cricket | handball | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, animation, satire, adventure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, salsa, jazz, d&b
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
2. the fan of d&b is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the fan of funk##7
3. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of d&b and the person watching animation movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | adventure | satire | disaster  |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | funk  | d&b   | salsa |

