.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, fishing, rock-climbing, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, cricket, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's hobby is chess##7
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | fishing | gardening | chess       | rock-climbing |
| Sport   | rowing      | ice-hockey   | cricket | lacrosse  |

