.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, sudoku, puzzles, gardening
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, colombian, argentine, egyptian
1. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the indian is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the egyptian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
5. the egyptian is on the left of the argentine##1
6. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the egyptian##5
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | fishing   | gardening | sudoku |
| Nationality   | indian      | colombian | egyptian      | argentine |

