.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, tea, fanta
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, polish, indian, spanish
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the indian##1
2. the indian is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the polish is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the spanish##3
6. the spanish is somewhere between the pakistani and the polish##7
7. the indian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk      | tea | fanta     |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | spanish | polish   | indian |

