.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, potato, cabbage, peach
There are 4 different nationalities: french, italian, mexican, australian
1. the french is on the far left##1
2. the person eating potato is on the left of the italian##1
3. the person eating peach is on the far left or far right##3
4. the australian is somewhere between the person eating mango and the person eating cabbage##7
5. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
6. the australian is on the left or right of the mexican##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | peach    | mango   | potato | cabbage  |
| Nationality   | french | mexican | australian    | italian |

