2. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
3. the canadian is the owner of the pony##1
4. the french is somewhere between the canadian and the australian##7
5. the brazilian is on the left of the australian##1
6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | french | brazilian | australian |
| Pet           | pony   | snake    | rat       | fish  |

