2. the coach is on the right of the designer##1
3. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the designer##3
4. the designer is on the right of the fan of blues##1
5. the coach is somewhere between the fan of blues and the librarian##7
6. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | manager | designer | coach | librarian |
| Music-Genre   | blues         | hip-hop      | indie | soul            |

