.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, animation, spy, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: ferret, pony, horse, goldfish
1. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person watching comedy movies and the owner of the goldfish##7
2. the person watching animation movies is not the owner of the horse##6
3. the owner of the pony is not the person watching spy movies##6
4. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
5. the person watching comedy movies is the owner of the ferret##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | fantasy | animation | spy |
| Pet           | ferret    | pony   | goldfish  | horse      |

