.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel, western, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, reggae, hip-hop, dubstep
1. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the fan of reggae##2
6. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the person watching time-travel movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | scientific | time-travel | western   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | hip-hop      | country      | dubstep |

