3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5
6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is cooking##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | cooking | singing | chess | reading |
| Sport   | skateboarding  | surfing    | handball    | snowboarding  |

