The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, car, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person driving the roller##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the person driving the car##6
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the car is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
7. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | card-games | skydiving | drawing | magic-tricks |
| Transport   | roller   | taxi      | car        | jet-ski  |

