.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, sprite, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, funk, reggae, pop
1. the fan of funk is in an even position##4
2. the fan of pop is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the fan of reggae##7
3. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
4. the fan of reggae is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the fan of funk##5
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | coffee   | sprite | almond-milk | soy-milk   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | reggae   | pop | funk |

