.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, chinchilla, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, jet-ski, van, helicopter
1. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the owner of the pony##7
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | pony    | chinchilla | rat     | mouse |
| Transport   | van | helicopter  | jet-ski | trike |

 